320
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:33,840
<font color="#ffff00">Kurasa kita tak ada hubungan apapun lagi.</font>

321
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:38,888
<font color="#ffff00">Kita putus secara resmi.</font>

322
00:34:40,585 --> 00:34:42,161
<font color="#ffff00">Selamat tinggal.</font>

323
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:47,440
<font color="#ffff00">Dao Ming-si.</font>

324
00:35:21,241 --> 00:35:22,560
<font color="#ffff00">Jika begitu...</font>

325
00:35:32,587 --> 00:35:36,400
