335
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:44,939
<font color="#ffff00">Aku hampir merusak keluarga sahabatku.</font>

336
00:37:45,039 --> 00:37:46,860
<font color="#ffff00">Hampir kubuang harga diri dan martabatku.</font>

337
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:49,680
<font color="#ffff00">Bersikap jujur padamu tanpa
