364
00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:17,892
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Karena kamu, aku percaya cinta itu ada</i></font>

365
00:40:17,992 --> 00:40:23,138
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Di matamu, di dalam hidupku</i></font>

366
00:40:25,802 --> 00:40:31,680
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Aku mengerti, aku menanti adanya cinta</i></font>

367
00:40:50,481 --> 00:40:52,420
<font color="#ffff00">A Si, kenapa hari ini
