397
00:43:14,046 --> 00:43:15,921
<font color="#ffff00">Terserah kamu mau berbuat apa.</font>

398
00:43:16,887 --> 00:43:20,599
<font color="#ffff00">A Si, serahkanlah Shan-cai padaku.</font>

399
00:43:34,440 --> 00:43:37,960
<font color="#ffff00">Tidakkah kalian merasa
