400
00:43:39,440 --> 00:43:42,460
<font color="#ffff00">Satu bodoh. Satunya lagi tukang tidur.</font>

401
00:43:42,560 --> 00:43:44,480
<font color="#ffff00">Tak pernah berpisah.</font>

402
00:43:46,000 --> 00:43:47,400
<font color="#ffff00">A Si.</font>

403
00:43:54,440 --> 00:43:59,200
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Katakanlah sesuatu,
